      "claim_as_stated": "Vaccines cause autism",
      "atomic_claims": [
        "Childhood vaccines do not cause autism.",
        "Vaccines do not contribute to the cause of autism.",
        "Vaccines have no role in the onset of autism.",
        "Autism is a neurodevelopmental difference usually present at birth, before vaccination begins.",
        "Vaccines are not associated with autism.",
        "The scientific community has researched this very thoroughly and there\u2019s no evidence that childhood vaccines cause autism.",
        "The US CDC says claims that vaccines cause autism are not evidence-based.",
        "The scientific evidence overwhelmingly shows that vaccines do not cause or are even correlated with autism.",
        "Scientists have yet to find a single cause for autism, and many believe that the disorder is multifactorial."
      ],
