      "why_people_believe_it": "People find the claim that vaccines cause autism psychologically compelling because it aligns with their desire to understand complex health issues through simple explanations, and it taps into fears about the safety of medical interventions for children. It also feeds into a broader mistrust in scientific institutions and pharmaceutical companies.",
